title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2003-2007 Infiniti G35 (Coupe) Head Light Installation Guide
description: This video will show you how to remove your factory headlights and install a set of Spyder custom aftermarket headlights in an easy to understand, step-by-step manner and also includes how to transfer your OEM HID (high intensity discharge) bulbs and ballasts to your new headlight.
